# Ignore local .claude tooling (launch.json, settings.local.json, …) but version
# the skills so they travel with the repo. Note: the parent dir must be matched with
# `.claude/*` (not `.claude/`) for the negation below to take effect — git can't
# re-include a path whose parent directory is itself excluded.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/

# .env variants (keep example files tracked)
.env.*
!.env.example
.vercel
.env*

# local scratch scripts (not part of the site)
test_chat.*

# personal git cheat sheet (not part of the site)
GIT_CHEATSHEET.md
